11 PW1 定你地幾個比我，幾個打我  <br />\n02:20:14 不知名警察 證物嚟嘅，爛撚咗，攔撚咗  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n02:20:19 不知名警察 喂，依度仲有粒  <br />\n02:20:20 不知名警察 仲有無？仲有無？齊晒齊哂，比我，比我。家誠，證物"},{"pid":"80e1eead2181eb204bc8ab34e747dcc671d79e0c","tid":2392343,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8e8f80f3524402b78c6ff562fd19763920c71063","tid":2392343,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T17:08:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T17:12:48.000Z","msg":"夠晒似黑警啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/VC1pRxENrtg/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FVC1pRxENrtg%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=590020e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a2f2bd7bdccd14be77448ac5dc1f6c4fe1124c8","tid":2392343,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T17:14:41.000Z","msg":"原創：香港特別行政區  訴 黃明偉<br />\n_________________<br />\n裁判法院上訴案件2020年第223號<br />\n(原九龍城裁判法院刑事案件2019年第2771號)<br />\n<a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/ju/ju_frame.jsp?DIS=133250&amp;currpage=T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Flrs%2Fcommon%2Fju%2Fju_frame.jsp%3FDIS%3D133250%26currpage%3DT&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrfsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=f4d4d3dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/ju/ju_frame.jsp?DIS=133250&amp;currpage=T</a>"},{"pid":"0ee5875e69ea36ba7a95b594493ec4ac5a4f0c16","tid":2392343,"uid":309806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T17:19:16.000Z","msg":"豪哥： 走呀，我叫你走呀"},{"pid":"4a4397b2bfdf41e4a09014cb0129803aa834b61f","tid":2392343,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{